# Copy to .envrc and fill in values, then run: direnv allow
#
# GITHUB_TOKEN is used for:
#   - GitHub Releases API (bump-nvim-plugins.go)
#   - GitHub Models API / gpt-4o (analyze-plugin.mjs)
#   - gh CLI calls inside analyze-plugin.mjs
#
# A classic PAT with no scopes is enough for public repos.
# For private repos add: repo (read)
# The Models API requires the token to be tied to an account
# with an active GitHub Copilot subscription.

export GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_your_token_here
